songs.title: Dis Side (Demo)
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
Yeah, yeah

[Verse 1]
Let me tell ya lil' story ’bout dis side
You really couldn't make it on dis side
I want it now on dis side
Nothin' but us the niggas on dis side, yeah
Hangin’ with a broad on dis side
Night, late night on dis side
You never came around 'round midnight
Now we're hangin' out on dis side

[Chorus]
Dis side, dis side
Dis side, dis side, dis side
Dis side, dis side
Dis side, dis side, d'yeah

[Verse 2]
Lost a lot of money on dis side
Made a lot of money on dis side
Had my first kiss on dis side
Word around town 'round midnight
Lately I been comin' 'round dis side
Tryna get back on dis side
Tryna get back to on dis side
Niggas ain’t on on dis side
And I wanna know at midnight
Want it, want it done at midnight
Hangin’ on the block, gotta hit nine
Then I gotta know I gotta right
How does somethin' not wanna live this?
Settin’ all the vibes on a lit night
Never wanna, never wanna think twice
Only way to live, only live life is on dis side

[Chorus]
Dis side, dis side
Dis side, dis side, dis side
Dis side, dis side
Dis side, dis side, dis side

[Verse 3]
Only way, only way, only way dis side
Dis side, dis side, dis side
That's right, that's right
You never pulled up on midnight, midnight
Midnight, midnight
You know I like my lean poured just right, just right
On dis side
You find everything you need, everything you need
Everything inbetween, I veil these jeans
I used to pull up on the mean, I used to pull up on the team
I gotta lo-lonely, got fours on a bomb bean
Hoes on and they lonely, hoes on they lonely

[Chorus]
On dis side, on dis side, on dis side
Dis side, dis side
Dis side, dis side, yeah, dis side
Dis side, dis side, dis side
Dis side, dis side
